1.
[a-z] - allow only a to z lowercase
[A-Z] - allow only A to Z- upper case 

a to z or A to Z : matches the single character in the range between a anz z  
- g - global modifier - All matches (don't return after first match )
- m - modifier - multi line - causes ^ and $ to match the begin/ end of each line ( not only begin / end of string ) 

2.
^[a-z] or ^[A-Z]
matches any character except a-z/A-Z range
